  "system": {
    "description": "<p>A PR5 cosmic-tier villain who was once a paragon — possibly the most powerful this city has ever produced. Warden now believes that powered individuals are an evolutionary error that generates suffering for everyone around them, including themselves. He does not want to rule. He wants to end the paragon era entirely, and he has both the power and the patience to try. He is not cruel. He is thorough.</p>",
